snippet.title: Dunjungle Trailer
snippet.description:
A 2d action-packed roguelite about an ape adventuring into a mysterious jungle to find his lost human friend. Explore ever-changing dungeons, fight weird enemies and gear up with lots of weapons you can combine for a new experience every run. Explore, fight, die, and repeat!

Play the demo now, and wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1589570/Dunjungle/
